- Normal footer: topY ≈ 43-44, height ≈ 9
- When buggy: topY extends to ~135, height ≈ 100
- Page height is likely around 297mm = 842pt (A4)

Current threshold: height/3 ≈ 280pt — the note at 135pt passes easily.

