height/8 ≈ 105pt — the note at 135pt would be filtered out. Footer at 44pt passes. This seems safe.

But I'm worried about US Letter where height=792, so height/8=99. A footer could legitimately be at 100pt from bottom.

Let me try height/7 ≈ 120/113. Note at 135 > 120, so it gets filtered. Footer at 44 < 120, passes. US Letter: 792/7 = 113. Still might be tight.

