- Sorted in descending order of topY → top of page first
- So in the sorted list: index 0 = top of page, index last = bottom of page

The footer sublist: `pageContents.subList(pageContents.size() - currentIndex, pageContents.size())`
- These are the last `currentIndex` elements → the bottommost elements
